Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.74,0:01:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,12 Rick Doms from Admiral Dozle's\Nforces were eradicated...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...thanks to the teamwork of the\NWhite Base crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,However, their ship had to return\Nto Side 6 without being repaired...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...at the floating dock\Noutside the Side's airspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.09,0:01:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For the White Base,\Nthere was no safe haven.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.22,0:01:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A Fateful Encounter
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,0:02:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back. How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,More formalities about our stay.\NThey want us out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.51,0:02:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But... the Tianem Fleet\Nhasn't given us movement orders yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the enemy could be lying in wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When do you expect Amuro back?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In 2 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is it something important?\N- Yes... I'm quite sure it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish maintenance in three hours.\NWe're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Man! They could have at least\Ngiven me a weather schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.03,0:03:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean...\NI didn't mean to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... about that bird...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you fond of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could hate beautiful things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could hate beautiful things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could hate beautiful things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...beautiful things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think there is anyone\Nwho hates beautiful things?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.66,0:04:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it sad to watch them\Ngrow old and perish?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sure it is...\NBut what I wanted to ask was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It's stopped raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes are so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure we should leave\NConscon's group?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Admiral Dozle and Conscon only\Nhave their eyes on the immediate enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the case with Lady Kycilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's looking at the direction\Nof the overall war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.65,0:05:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what is at Side 6, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be entering battle soon.\NYou'll find out then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's enter the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Char's Zanzibar\Nis docking at Side 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Char is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Always doing whatever he pleases.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now there's a big surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're docked in the same port\Nas an enemy warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a scene that could only happen\Nin a neutral Side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a comic book!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we invite the enemy over\Nand throw a party or something. Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- I just can't forgive them...!\N- Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "where"?\NMr. Ryu's killers are right in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what consequences we'd face\Nif we fought at this Side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be departing very soon.\NNo one is to leave the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of maintenance to do still.\NEveryone, to your stations now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just be sure you don't prolong\Nthe duration of your stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- Now, the weapon seals...\N- I'm aware of the penalties.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. And I don't want any trouble\Nwith the Federation Forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already informed my men.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.24,0:07:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? I'm so happy\Nyou've become the Gundam pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The part I gave you last night!\NHow was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The new device I handed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:08:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It had tremendous effects... didn't it?\NAmuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yeah.\NOf... course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it worked great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll develop more. And more!\NI'll concentrate on new upgrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it did,\NI made it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My next one will be even...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What good are shelter capsules, anyway?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad, are mobile suits more important{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Send out the trailer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You go to the White Base, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.16,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have taken the shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Char?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that. Unfortunately,\Nthe driver's still a novice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that. I thought\Nyou'd be able to dodge it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to tow your car out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.61,0:10:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro. Amuro Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange... I feel as though\NI've heard your name before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, I know you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.17,0:10:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know who you are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.10,0:10:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax. I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:10:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's your name?\N- Char Aznable. I'm a soldier, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Char!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah! Step on the gas! But gently!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is Char.said.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it easy. Got it, Lalah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\NStand back, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've never met him before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So how did I know that he was Char?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.11,0:11:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that girl...he called her Lalah.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Me? I'm 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? You're still young.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.09,0:11:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand why you'd be nervous\Nin front of an enemy soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But it would be nice if you\Nat least said thanks, Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Of course. Thank you very much.\NI'd better go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that boy so nervous about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably recognized your name, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Char, the Red Comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have been afraid of you... I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.65,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation hasn't changed at all\Nsince we arrived here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No sense in worrying about it, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. We send the Gundam out in front...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. We've been waiting for you.\NYou wanted something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually... I was hoping\NI could help you out personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Cameron...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a private ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can use it to escort you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If a Side 6 ship were shielding you,\Nthe Zeons couldn't open fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I do appreciate the thought, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Cameron. What do you expect\Nby doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shocked to hear you asking\Nsuch a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather you didn't interfere\Nin our business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.33,0:13:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mirai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't get off this ship,\Nthen at least accept my help...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's not interfering,\NI don't know what is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be insulting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just trying to convince me\Nthat you can be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.60,0:13:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But you weren't there when I was\Nsuffering the most. It's too late now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I'm able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.42,0:13:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- Lieutenant!\N- You!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This man is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he's offering to take this risk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This may be a neutral Side...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...but one stray missile, and he's dead!\NYou understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you stand there quietly\Nwhile she's hassling you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to hit her. If we talked...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're serious, you'd have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so barbaric.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Mr. Cameron.\NIt's all about determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Ensign?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Sleggar...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you haven't changed your mind...\NI would like to accept your offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.60,0:14:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Please let me do this... Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here they come.\N- But a Side 6 civilian ship is next to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.85,0:14:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes all kinds, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Have the Rick Doms launched?\N- They should be ready now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Trojan Horse has changed course.\NIt's escaping in the opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.64,0:15:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Deploy the Rick Doms at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind airspace violations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be fine!\NThe fighting will be outside the borders!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand being laughed at\Nby an upstart like Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This wasn't part of our deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to compensate me very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Cameron. We're already at the edge\Nof our airspace. If we go further...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bright! There are Zeon mobile suits!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done enough, Mr. Cameron.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. Not until you leave our airspace...y.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.90,0:16:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- Did something happen up on the bridge?\N- It's no concern for a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'll be at the main cannons.\N- Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Approaching Side 6 perimeter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Cameron.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please pull back.but to fight them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cameron... Thank you.feelings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cameron, thank you.\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.06,0:16:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give my best to your father and mother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm turning back.\N- Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Fly by the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Open hatch!\NPrepare to deploy the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Guncannon and G-Fighter!\NStand by!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,White Base, go to full combat speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Engaging in anti-air combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Rick Doms,\Ncommence the attack now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mega beam cannons, hold your fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, stray beams might\Nenter Side 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's started!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The battle's... started...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A TV crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Jamice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- You think you're so hot...!\N- Wait, Kai! Ignore the mobile suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All the main cannons need to do\Nis keep the enemy ship at bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit the enemy ships from the side!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Until then, use only\Nthe missiles for defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!\NIt just can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost like he's predicting our moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's just a fluke! Just luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Our only hope is to confuse him!\NLet's use our favorite tactic!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see... how they'll move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is not a TV drama.i\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Federation and Zeonn outer space.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in the White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me the Gundam!\NShow me how it's doing in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.74,0:19:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. There!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Amuro!\NWhat are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant! Enemy ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know. Now just watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat. This Is a real battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The fighting is going onrs.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Federation's White Base{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...against 3 Zeon ships.ing you well?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.37,0:20:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch this very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Real combat isn't nearly as\Nattractive as a TV drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As witnesses to this conflict...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...we must all give thought to the position{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He fell for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.19,0:20:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait a second! I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro's intuition is especially keen today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm running out of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't use the beam rifle\NI've got to switch to close combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How can just one ship cause us\Nthis much trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Char is watching us! Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ram into them!! Ram the Chivvay\Nright into the side of that Trojan Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Musais have been destroyed, andng.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As there are no mobile suits In sight,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The white mobile suit is going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? But the Gundam's not even on screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.48,0:21:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you took a woman like me\Nunder your wing, isn't it, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're perceptive, Lalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're ramming us.'re getting desperate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's their vital spot?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Enemy below!\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- No! Portside!\N- Left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,See, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.86,0:22:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NWay to go, Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to my new device!\NThe Gundam's the real deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray for the Earth Federation!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We can head back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.55,0:22:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.26,0:22:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please make It through this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.24,0:23:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Side... 6...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.42,0:23:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Earth Federation Forces stage\Na full-scale attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...against Space Fortress Solomon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.51,0:23:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,At the vanguard of the Tianem Fleet,\Nthe White Base cuts through the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.56,0:23:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,For the first time, Amuro and the crew\Nrisk their lives in the middle of a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.36,0:23:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NThe Glory of Solomon
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.69,0:23:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.84,0:23:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Glory of Solomon
